OL,11,FGeorge Thorley, of Moorbottom in
OL,12,FCleckheaton, , was sentenced to 27
OL,13,Fyears in prison at on Wednesday, for
OL,14,F32 offences including rape between the
OL,15,F1970s and 1990s in locations across
OL,16,FEngland.
OL,18,FThe 74-year-old was described as
OL,19,Fposing a "genuine danger" to children
OL,20,Fby detectives investigating his
OL,21,Foffending in , and West Yorkshire.
